The other likely sub-categories are cs.GT (Game Theory) which includes topics related to voting and social choice, cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) which includes topics related to decision-making and optimization, cs.LG (Machine Learning) which includes topics related to learning from data, and cs.CC (Computational Complexity) which includes topics related to the complexity of algorithms and problems.
